  <!-- Introducción de la actividad -->  
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="narrative-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>The purpose of this warm-up is for students to notice that figures composed of multiple arrays can be decomposed into smaller arrays, and that this is a strategy to determine the total number of dots. This will be helpful in later lessons when students decompose figures into rectangles to find the total area.</p>
<p>When students find ways to decompose the given arrangements of dots to find the number of dots, they practice looking for and making use of structure (MP7).</p>
  </paragraphs>

